flowchart LR
    App["Application Tier<br/>API / Services"] --> DBLayer

    DBLayer["DB Access Layer<br/>Query Classifier<br/>Normal vs Heavy Queries"]

    %% Normal path
    DBLayer -->|"Writes<br/>INSERT / UPDATE / DELETE"| Master
    DBLayer -->|"Normal Reads<br/>OLTP Queries"| Master

    %% Heavy read path
    DBLayer -->|"Heavy Reads<br/>Reports / Analytics"| Slave

    Master["DB Master<br/>Primary<br/>OLTP + Writes"]
    Slave["DB Slave<br/>Read Replica<br/>Heavy Queries"]

    %% Replication
    Master -->|"Real-time Replication<br/>Binlog / WAL"| Slave
